text: Dharma Prasad Ghimire () is a Nepalese politician, belonging to the Communist Party of Nepal. In the 2008 Constituent Assembly election he was elected from the Jhapa 1 constituency, winning 15276 votes.Ca Election report ==References== Category:Living people Category:Communist Party of Nepal (Maoist Centre) politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Khas people Category:Members of the Nepalese Constituent Assembly
